Package: arbalist
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2023-04-04
Title: Bringing ArchR to Bioconductor
Description: 
    Implements the core algorithms inside ArchR using C++ bindings to DelayedArrays,
    in preparation for submission to Bioconductor.
